00:00:00.250 --> 00:00:04.370
Grilling is a summertime favorite but no one wants to be the guy that can’t get the grill

00:00:04.370 --> 00:00:08.800
started. One of the simplest "mikehacks" you
can use is to light off a handful of potato

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:14.099
chips. Not only are they delicious, they can
be surprisingly flammable as well. But in

00:00:14.099 --> 00:00:17.850
this project, you get to keep your snacks
intact, because we're hacking a new breed

00:00:17.850 --> 00:00:21.570
of party roasters, and it all starts, with
your empty drink cans.

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:34.320
We’re all familiar with the term “lifehacks” but this summer, the guys at mike’s hard lemonade asked me

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:37.390
to help put a refreshing twist on it with
what they’re calling “mikehacks"

00:00:37.390 --> 00:00:38.960
noun: mikehack; plural noun: mikehacks; noun:
mike hack; plural noun: mike hacks

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:42.399
1. basically a lifehack that makes any social
